reviews.text: The food is so good! The flavors are awesome and even the presentation is amazing. Finally, the staff are friendly and helpful, so this is a really great place to go to for dinner.
Fantastic vegetarian chinese. Manager Ricky is a super host. For dedicated vegetarians, none of the cookware touches meat products. Highly recommended.
中式素食，午市套餐59包茶及糖水，要求不高都係一個比較不錯的選擇。😄

十分精緻的素食菜式, 但是糖水就不要試了
佛誕當日，停了不少菜式，只做套餐。
食物味道不錯，服務員態度很好，環境舒服，價錢不貴
